  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game introduction</h2><br>\"Hello World\" is a 2D platform,adventure and puzzle games. The player will play as a people who has strayed into the computer world, explore the computer world with the cursor sprite. During the exploration, you will have a series of interesting interactions with, garbage files, Word documents, PowerPoint documents, Excel documents, anti-virus software, blinking cursors while typing and even binary 0 and 1 in computer. Wish you a good journey!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game presentation</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/f96e7030ad23d1a969793e110967400b.poster.avif?t=1727416288\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/f96e7030ad23d1a969793e110967400b.webm?t=1727416288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/f96e7030ad23d1a969793e110967400b.mp4?t=1727416288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>I stumbled into <strong>the world of computers</strong>! ? This place is different than I expected......<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Folder</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/e810489544581d3cacca1d7cbae4857a.poster.avif?t=1727416288\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/e810489544581d3cacca1d7cbae4857a.webm?t=1727416288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/e810489544581d3cacca1d7cbae4857a.mp4?t=1727416288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>I should be <strong>inside the folder</strong>, I must try to change the folder size to enter the Word document.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Word Document</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/1198f6e3278c6077279e2bf66fcf5762.poster.avif?t=1727416288\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/1198f6e3278c6077279e2bf66fcf5762.webm?t=1727416288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/1198f6e3278c6077279e2bf66fcf5762.mp4?t=1727416288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>I am in a <strong>Word document</strong>! Are they binary zeros and binary ones in the computer?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Excel Document</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/70c9de27fbe2b0c208d44cb6593e8da0.poster.avif?t=1727416288\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/70c9de27fbe2b0c208d44cb6593e8da0.webm?t=1727416288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/70c9de27fbe2b0c208d44cb6593e8da0.mp4?t=1727416288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Excel Document？It looks very interesting!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/b057becad6c6d81fa81e105630bbf563.poster.avif?t=1727416288\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2802140/extras/b057becad6c6d81fa81e105630bbf563.webm?t=1727416288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=